#MEM id=content-suggestion-engine source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Marketing/kai/skills/custom/content-suggestion-engine/SKILL.md
M|content-suggestion-engine|> Owner: Kai (anl) · Co-authors: Nate (Growth), Lena (Brand), Kahneman (Bias rv)
M|content-suggestion-engine|> Last updated: 2026-05-20
M|content-suggestion-engine|> vtr scope: Novizio · Hourbour
M|content-suggestion-engine|CSE is a self-learning cnt scoring system. It generates pitch recommendations,
M|content-suggestion-engine|scores them against live signals, tracks whether ap pitches overperform or
M|content-suggestion-engine|underperform benchmarks, and adjusts signal weights over time.
M|content-suggestion-engine|The loop is:
M|content-suggestion-engine|```
M|content-suggestion-engine|Signal → Score → Pitch → ap → Calendar → Post → Measure → Reflect → Re-weight
M|content-suggestion-engine|```
M|content-suggestion-engine|| Table | Purpose |
M|content-suggestion-engine||-------|---------|
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `content_performance` | One row per ap pitch. Tracks outcome, actual metrics, benchmark delta. |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `signal_reliability` | Per-signal accuracy score. Updated after each measurement. |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `scoring_weight_history` | Audit trail of E/R/G/B/T weight changes. |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `pitch_pass_reasons` | Records why a pitch was dismissed. Penalises unreliable signals. |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| Code | Dimension | What it measures |
M|content-suggestion-engine||------|-----------|-----------------|
M|content-suggestion-engine|| E | Engagement Signal | cp engagement delta, trending formats |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| R | Revenue Correlation | SEO search volume, buyer intent keywords |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| G | Growth Fit | Funnel stage alignment, audience match |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| B | Brand Resonance | Tone fit, brand voice coherence |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| T | Timing | Platform trend window, urgency signals |
M|content-suggestion-engine|Default weights: `E=0.25 · R=0.25 · G=0.20 · B=0.15 · T=0.15`
M|content-suggestion-engine|Weights are vtr-specific and drift over time as CSE learns.
M|content-suggestion-engine|| Signal | Trigger condition |
M|content-suggestion-engine||--------|-----------------|
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `GAP_OPPORTUNITY` | cp posts in a format we haven't tried — high eng, low our coverage |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `PROVEN_FORMAT` | Format we've done before with above-benchmark result |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `SEO_WINDOW` | Keyword search volume spike + low SERP competition |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `URGENCY_WINDOW` | Trending topic with <72h relevance window |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `FUNNEL_FIX` | Funnel drop-off detected at a specific stage (Kai identifies from GA4) |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| Route | Method | Purpose |
M|content-suggestion-engine||-------|--------|---------|
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `/api/cnt-intelligence` | POST | gen a new pitch batch (5 pitches) |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `/api/cnt-intelligence` | GET | Fetch current pitches + batch status |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `/api/cnt-intelligence` | PATCH | Update pitch status (ap / passed) |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `/api/cnt-performance` | POST | Record a pitch going live (create perf row) |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `/api/cnt-performance` | GET | Fetch pending (≥7d old, unmeasured) + stage |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `/api/cnt-performance` | GET `?pitchId=` | Fetch single record for Studio outcome banner |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `/api/cnt-performance` | PATCH `action:link_calendar` | Write `calendar_entry_id` back to perf row |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `/api/cnt-performance` | PATCH `action:measure` | Submit actual metrics, compute outcome |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `/api/cnt-performance/measure` | POST | Cron T+7 auto-measurement trigger |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `/api/signal-reliability` | GET | Fetch per-signal accuracy scores |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `/api/weight-proposal` | GET | Fetch pending E/R/G/B/T weight change proposals |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `/api/weight-proposal` | POST | ap or reject a weight proposal |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| `/api/cse-reflection` | POST | Cron weekly reflection — proposes weight changes |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| Stage | Condition | Scoring source |
M|content-suggestion-engine||-------|-----------|----------------|
M|content-suggestion-engine|| 0 | No measured posts | Industry benchmarks (8K–12K follower cohort) |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| 1 | 1–4 measured posts | Low-confidence blend: 70% benchmarks + 30% own data |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| 2 | 5+ measured posts | Own historical data primary |
M|content-suggestion-engine|1. **gen** — Kai calls `/api/cnt-intelligence` POST → 5 pitches with CSE scores
M|content-suggestion-engine|2. **ap** — User clicks ap on a pitch card in mkt → cnt tab
M|content-suggestion-engine|- PATCH `/api/cnt-intelligence` (status: ap)
M|content-suggestion-engine|- POST `/api/cnt-performance` (creates perf row with pitch_id, signal_type, score_at_suggestion)
M|content-suggestion-engine|- Calendar modal opens pre-filled
M|content-suggestion-engine|3. **Schedule** — User saves the calendar entry
M|content-suggestion-engine|- POST `/api/cnt-calendar` → returns entry.id
M|content-suggestion-engine|- PATCH `/api/cnt-performance` `action:link_calendar` → writes calendar_entry_id back
M|content-suggestion-engine|4. **Post** — cnt goes live. User marks status → `posted` in calendar
M|content-suggestion-engine|5. **Measure** — 7 days after post_at:
M|content-suggestion-engine|- Cron fires `/api/cnt-performance/measure` → auto-check for pending
M|content-suggestion-engine|- OR user clicks "Measure X posts" pill in mkt → cnt tab → enters actual metrics
M|content-suggestion-engine|- PATCH `/api/cnt-performance` → computes outcome (overperformed / met / underperformed)
M|content-suggestion-engine|- Triggers `update_signal_reliability` RPC → adjusts signal accuracy
M|content-suggestion-engine|6. **Reflect** — Weekly cron fires `/api/cse-reflection`
M|content-suggestion-engine|- Analyses recent outcomes vs signal types
M|content-suggestion-engine|- If a signal type has >70% accuracy → propose weight increase (weight-proposal table)
M|content-suggestion-engine|- User approves or rejects in the weight proposal panel on the pitch board
M|content-suggestion-engine|7. **Re-weight** — ap weight changes take effect on next pitch generation
M|content-suggestion-engine|| Surface | Location | What it shows |
M|content-suggestion-engine||---------|----------|---------------|
M|content-suggestion-engine|| Pitch cards | mkt → cnt → pitch board | CSE score, E/R/G/B/T bars, hook A/B, growth hypothesis |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| Stage banner | mkt → cnt (top of pitch board) | Stage 0/1/2 label, "Measure X posts" pill when pending |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| Measure Now modal | Triggered from stage banner | Metric input (views/likes/comments/shares/saves/reach) |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| Weight proposal panel | Below pitch board | Pending E/R/G/B/T change proposals with ap/reject |
M|content-suggestion-engine|| Outcome banner | Creative Studio (top, when opened from pitch) | overperformed / met / underperformed + delta vs benchmark |
M|content-suggestion-engine|1. Never gen pitches without checking `signal_reliability` first — penalised signals (accuracy < 0.40) get a 0.5× weight multiplier.
M|content-suggestion-engine|2. Always include `growthHypothesis` in `fullProposal` — it's the key field that connects to measurement.
M|content-suggestion-engine|3. When proposing weight changes: only propose if ≥3 data points exist for that signal type. Fewer than 3 = noise.
M|content-suggestion-engine|4. Stage 0 → industry benchmarks only. Never invent own-history data.
M|content-suggestion-engine|5. After each `cse-reflection` run, save the proposed weight rationale to `scoring_weight_history` regardless of ap status.